history.content: EE 120 touches a bunch of subfields in EE and is not too heavy.

I am a 2nd Year currently taking CS61C, CS70, my R1B, and another breadth. 

I went to the first lecture and it was not what I was expecting at all, and it really does nothing for me so I was thinking of dropping it. I know the semester has already started, but is there any possibility I could put a different technical class in its place? I was thinking of EE C145, but I am not sure if it would work given how time consuming I hear 61c and 70 are. 

Are you even allowed to enroll in classes after the first week?

Please let me know if you have any suggestions!

Thanks!
history.subject: Dislike Breadth, Any Technical Recs?
